oesn\'t initialize Sentry** as required by the PRD/exec plan.\n4. **`packages/sh
ared-types/src/index.ts` doesn\'t export generated types**: The generated auth t
ypes exist in `packages/shared-types/src/generated/auth/` but aren\'t re-exporte
